reviewText:
I have mised feelings specially because of the lengh of the game. It is too short in my point of view.
But the bottom line is that I recommend this game.
Pros:
+ Non-stop action;
+ Different weapons and cars, ships, battle armor, etc;
+ Destructive environment;
Cons:
- Very short game;
- Poor replay;
- Poor story;

